kroaches, ants, fleas, moths, squirrels, pigeons, gulls and bird control, moles, rabbits, foxes, woodworm, fumigation, and commercial contract pest management. The service works for domestic pest control, commercial pest control, agricultural pest control, landlord pest services, and local authority subcontract work equally well." },
